                    "Manipulate) Habits </span></div><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"center01\">&nbsp;</p><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"toc_part\"><span class=\"hlink\" href=\"Duhi_9780679603856_epub_p03_r1.htm\"><strong>PART THREE </strong><br /><strong>The Habits of Societies </strong></span></div><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"toc_chap\"><span class=\"hlink\" href=\"Duhi_9780679603856_epub_c08_r1.htm\">8. SADDLEBACK CHURCH AND THE MONTGOMERY BUS BOYCOTT <br />How Movements Happen </span></div><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"toc_chap\"><span class=\"hlink\" href=\"Duhi_9780679603856_epub_c09_r1.htm\">9. THE NEUROLOGY OF FREE WILL <br />Are We Responsible for Our Habits? </span></div><p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"center01\">&nbsp;</p><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"toc_bm\"><p class=\"center0\"><span class=\"hlink\" href=\"Duhi_9780679603856_epub_app_r1.htm\">APPENDIX <br />A Reader’s Guide to Using These Ideas </span></p><p class=\"center0\"><span class=\"hlink\" href=\"Duhi_9780679603856_epub_ack_r1.htm\">Acknowledgments </span></p><p class=\"center0\"><span class=\"hlink\" href=\"Duhi_9780679603856_epub_bm1_r1.htm\">A Note on Sources </span></p><p class=\"center0\"><span class=\"hlink\" href=\"Duhi_9780679603856_epub_nts_r1.htm\">Notes </span></p></div>"
